snippet.title: Tenders Fight - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Game:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2374010/Tenders_Fight/

Tenders Fight is a fast-paced FPS Game. 

FIGHT against mutant chickens, 
DASH through them, 
BREAK through doors and 
Find your way to Earth. 

As the last spaceship survivor, use your boxing skills to 
DESTROY EVERYTHING! 
These chickens will test your abilities to their limits, can you defeat them?

Game:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2374010/Tenders_Fight/

Music used:
Turbo - Uranus Flash
https://youtu.be/Jr4dHIHPjYI
